title: Dolphins-Jaguars TNF Recap: Fitzmagic returns, Minshew struggles, Tank for Trevor back on? (Football 9/25)
description:
Did Week 3 of Thursday Night Football live up to hype or was it exactly what you expected? The Dolphins defeated the Jaguars 31-13 as Ryan Fitzpatrick won this round of the budding rivalry against Gardner Minshew. Minshew was bad and the Jags have regressed since Week 1, but does that mean 'Tank for Trevor' is back on for Jacksonville? Meanwhile, Fitzmagic was in full force as Miami proved feisty again. Join the Pick Six Superfriends as they break down all the action.
